    "description": "Shyaway Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Marketplace Manager for our Kochi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Shyaway Digital Technologies:\nShyaway Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shyaway Digital Technologies!",
